  <!--
  This section drives what is shown in the Edit tab.
  "category" elements create branches in the tree structure.
  "parameter" elements are fields that the user can edit.
    Each parameter has a unique key (it MUST be unique!) identifying it.
    This allows Pawn files to be a simple, flat, dictionary of key/value pairs.
    Depending on the child elements of a parameter element, the parameter can be
    displayed using a variety of UI controls, such as a drop-down or a slider.
  -->
